# Istok, Pribaykalsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Istok () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Pribaykalsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 142 as of 2010. There are 4 streets.
Geography
Istok is located 110&nbsp;km northeast of Turuntayevo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Turka is the nearest rural locality.
